high_descs: Go to kitchen island.
Pick up the knife from counter.
Go to the loaf of bread on island.
Slice the loaf of bread.
Take the knife to fridge.
Put the knife in fridge.
Go back to the loaf of bread on island
Grab slice of bread off of counter.
Go to the microwave.
Cook slice of bread in microwave.
Go to the fridge with the slice of bread.
Put slice of bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put slice of cooked bread in fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the island counter on the left.
Pick up the large kitchen knife off of the counter.
Turn left and walk around the island counter to face the loaf of bread.
Slice the loaf of bread on the island counter.
Turn left to walk around the island counter and move to the fridge.
Put the knife into the freezer.
Turn around and walk around the island counter to face the loaf of bread to the left.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn to the right and walk around the island counter to the microwave.
Warm the bread in the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the right.
Put the slice of bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of warmed bread into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the island in front on its right side.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter.
Go around to the left side of the island.
Slice a half of the bread.
Turn left and go around the island to the refrigerator.
Place the bread in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the side of the island with the sliced bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn right and go around the island to the microwave in the right corner.
Heat the bread in the microwave and take it out.
Turn left and go back to the refrigerator.
Place the bread in the refrigerator  on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of bread in the fridge.
